      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should seek help or whatever, but it just feels so futile. like trying to fix a machine that's already been scrapped. there's no \"new way\" to live when the core of you is just... gone. why does everyone insist on dragging out the process when the end result is always the same? it's just misery.",
